Icedemon/Arcangel



As they stand in a portal on the a Vok planet they look up at a floating 
head and it speaks. "You both have turned on your creators. For that you 
should both be killed but we want to see if you all were a waist of time are 
worth our efforts. Icedemon you will be sent back to the planet and if you 
can clear the planet of all either good or evil you and arcangel can live. 
We have given you new weapons and let you carry the sign of you maximal 
people now go and see if you are worthy of our mercy."


In a blink of a eye Icedemon is lauched in a metal bubble back on to past 
earth.
